---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Mount Kush | POPIA Compliant" description="Mount Kush Privacy Policy. POPIA compliant. We respect your privacy and handle all personal information with discretion." noIndex={false}>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="display-md">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="margin-top:0.75rem; font-size:0.9rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">POPIA Compliant | Last updated: March 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--purple-deep);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose">

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong style="color:var(--gold-bright);">Your Privacy Matters</strong><br/>
          Mount Kush takes the protection of your personal information seriously. We collect only what we need, use it only for the purpose it was given, and never sell or share your data with third parties.
        </div>

        <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Mount Kush is a cannabis lifestyle retail brand operating in Johannesburg, South Africa. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store and protect your personal information in accordance with the Protection of Personal Information Act, 4 of 2013 (POPIA).</p>
        <p><strong style="color:white;">Information Officer:</strong> Mount Kush Management<br/>
        <strong style="color:white;">Contact:</strong> 063 926 0217 (WhatsApp)</p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following personal information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Name and surname</strong> — when you place an order or contact us</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">WhatsApp / phone number</strong> — for order processing and communication</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Loyalty programme details</strong> — first name and phone number for our Kush Rewards programme</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Order details</strong> — products ordered and purchase history</li>
          <li><strong style="color:white;">Payment reference</strong> — to confirm transactions (we do not store card details)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not collect government ID numbers, financial account details or sensitive personal information beyond what is necessary for transactions.</p>

        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Your information is used solely for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Processing and fulfilling your orders</li>
          <li>Communicating with you about your orders via WhatsApp</li>
          <li>Operating our Kush Rewards loyalty programme</li>
          <li>Responding to customer queries and complaints</li>
          <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We will not use your personal information for unsolicited marketing without your consent.</p>

        <h2>4. How We Protect Your Information</h2>
        <p>Mount Kush takes reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your personal information from unauthorised access, loss, or misuse. Orders and communications are handled through private WhatsApp conversations.</p>
        <p>We do not store your information on publicly accessible systems. Staff with access to customer data are bound by confidentiality obligations.</p>

        <h2>5. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, rent or share your personal information with third parties for marketing or any unrelated commercial purposes.</p>
        <p>We may share information only where required by law or with service providers directly involved in processing your order (such as payment processors), subject to appropriate data protection agreements.</p>

        <h2>6. Retention of Information</h2>
        <p>We retain personal information only for as long as necessary for the purpose for which it was collected, or as required by law. Loyalty programme data is retained for the duration of your membership and for a reasonable period thereafter.</p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights Under POPIA</h2>
        <p>As a data subject under POPIA, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Request access to the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your personal information</li>
          <li>Object to the processing of your personal information</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
          <li>Lodge a complaint with the Information Regulator of South Africa</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us on WhatsApp: 063 926 0217.</p>

        <h2>8. Cookies and Website Analytics</h2>
        <p>This website may use basic analytics to understand how visitors use the site. No personally identifiable information is collected through cookies. You may disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>

        <h2>9. Age Restriction</h2>
        <p>This website is intended for adults aged 18 years and older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from persons under 18. If we become aware that a minor has provided personal information, we will delete it promptly.</p>

        <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The date of the most recent revision is noted at the top of this page. Continued use of our website and services after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Policy.</p>

        <h2>11. Contact the Information Regulator</h2>
        <p>If you believe we have handled your personal information in violation of POPIA, you may lodge a complaint with the Information Regulator of South Africa:</p>
        <div class="info-box">
          <strong style="color:white;">Information Regulator (South Africa)</strong><br/>
          Website: <a href="https://inforegulator.org.za" target="_blank" rel="noopener">inforegulator.org.za</a><br/>
          Email: enquiries@inforegulator.org.za
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top:3rem; font-size:0.85rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">Questions about this Privacy Policy? Contact us on WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/27639260217" style="color:var(--gold-bright);">063 926 0217</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
